{"tid":2090601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，我唔想再見到任何勇武/ 中學以下既示威者....","createTime":"2020-07-02T08:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T11:23:40.000Z","uid":75100,"like":38,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1f2c42d605fd9ca3d3ef420ccbb8f06d01f2cd","tid":2090601,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"先唔講中學生心智根本未成熟，好多野可能都唔知/未搞清楚，被年齡相近既人煽動下，覺得自己係正義一方，成件事好熱血就去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果點? 好多咪比警察打柒，更甚既就好似之前何傳耀個個中五生咁，心存僥倖，覺得唔會真係有事，然後被人差d一槍打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無錯，多班後生仔出黎，係令到畫面好睇d方便打飛機，但18歲以下既，得罪講句有幾多個黃之鋒?有佢既覺悟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你唔係身懷超能力，定識魔法，唔該你地做返中學生既本份算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋勇武，睇到琴日單野我真係不吐不快，講真你係父母雙亡，月入1萬住劏房，一無所有既人，ok你係做勇武既最佳人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但現實係點? 好多後生仔被人up幾up，熱血上腦，就出火魔法，又用刀斬警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日條友係港大生，公屋仔黎講都算叻仔，可惜唔識權衡利弊，比熱血衝昏頭腦，而家人生盡毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被人捉到坐監個個係你，係警局比人打鳩個個係你，但連登班冷氣軍師呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係度話好嬲好嬲，然後轉個頭可能又去左打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我岩岩係fb見到朋友講琴日單野 :「我就係要呢d! 英雄!!」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但呢個人係有錢仔，我未撚見過佢出任何有dd危險既場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真仲有好多呢d人，我覺得仲嘔心過班藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲都係盲目撐，呢班黃絲明明自己中產，唔會肯捨身去做咩，就係咁煽動推人去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我講呢d預左比人鬧5毛，但勇武們你自己諗，為左呢班人值唔值得，自己承唔承擔到後果，唔好斬完警察又淆哂底，入警局比人虐待又係度嗌唔公平就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人幫到你，唔講遠，你諗下你斬完人想借錢買機票，所謂&quot;手足&quot; 敢唔敢冒風險幫你買</span></span>"},{"pid":"093f2e38fe52b7779dbe0e1ff715a91586d16846","tid":2090601,"uid":211110,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"五毛 分化撚 黑警<br />\n是但揀一樣"},{"pid":"330ee84e2d99bc923698b52389f52cf206a60a96","tid":2090601,"uid":59586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093f2e38fe52b7779dbe0e1ff715a91586d16846","tid":2090601,"uid":211110,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"五毛 分化撚 黑警<br />\n是但揀一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"f554f1cc5e99b8ba7912d2ef3b101eb566e04239","tid":2090601,"uid":197761,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3add9f037305a1590b402bf0f444e60b5f71e765","tid":2090601,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"Agree,代價太大"},{"pid":"0477a815d222fc23dc965d5ec7fcfa9231c92a4e","tid":2090601,"uid":344500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3add9f037305a1590b402bf0f444e60b5f71e765","tid":2090601,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"Agree,代價太大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"96a76ca454fddd4d8a707d25ca209d14bb49a7a5","tid":2090601,"uid":75100,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f554f1cc5e99b8ba7912d2ef3b101eb566e04239","tid":2090601,"uid":197761,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi